{"type":"message","id":"2e417a50","parentId":"9dd167a0","timestamp":"2026-03-09T09:01:18.781Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_Dcl8p7uSz2vbn5Metlb9d37W|fc_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae8c5deac88193886c196b691a94be","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-fetch-doc\ndescription: |\n  获取飞书云文档内容。返回文档的 Markdown 内容，支持处理文档中的图片、文件和画板（需配合 feishu_doc_media 工具）。\n---\n\n# feishu_mcp_fetch_doc\n\n获取飞书云文档的 Markdown 内容（Lark-flavored 格式）。\n\n## 重要：图片、文件、画板的处理\n\n**文档中的图片、文件、画板需要通过 `feishu_doc_media`（action: download）工具单独获取！**\n\n### 识别格式\n\n返回的 Markdown 中，媒体文件以 HTML 标签形式出现：\n\n- **图片**：\n  ```html\n  <image token=\"Z1FjxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxtnAc\" width=\"1833\" height=\"2491\" align=\"center\"/>\n  ```\n\n- **文件**：\n  ```html\n  <view type=\"1\">\n    <file token=\"Z1FjxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxtnAc\" name=\"skills.zip\"/>\n  </view>\n  ```\n\n- **画板**：\n  ```html\n  <whiteboard token=\"Z1FjxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxtnAc\"/>\n  ```\n\n### 获取步骤\n\n1. 从 HTML 标签中提取 `token` 属性值\n2. 调用 `feishu_doc_media` 下载：\n   ```json\n   {\n     \"action\": \"download\",\n     \"resource_token\": \"提取的token\",\n     \"resource_type\": \"media\",\n     \"output_path\": \"/path/to/save/file\"\n   }\n   ```\n\n## 参数\n\n- **`doc_id`**（必填）：支持直接传文档 URL 或 token\n  - 直接传 URL：`https://xxx.feishu.cn/docx/Z1FjxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxtnAc`（系统自动提取 token）\n  - 直接传 token：`Z1FjxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxtnAc`\n  - 知识库 URL/token 也支持：`https://xxx.feishu.cn/wiki/Z1FjxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxtnAc` 或 `Z1FjxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxtnAc`\n\n## Wiki URL 处理策略\n\n知识库链接（`/wiki/TOKEN`）背后可能是云文档、电子表格、多维表格等不同类型的文档。当不确定类型时, **不能直接假设是云文档**，必须先查询实际类型。\n\n### 处理流程\n\n1. **先调用 `feishu_wiki_space_node`（action: get）解析 wiki token**：\n   ```json\n   { \"action\": \"get\", \"token\": \"wiki_token_here\" }\n   ```\n2. **从返回的 `node` 中获取 `obj_type`（实际文档类型）和 `obj_token`（实际文档 token）**\n3. **根据 `obj_type` 调用对应工具**：\n\n| obj_type | 工具 | 传参 |\n|----------|------|------|\n| `docx` | `feishu_mcp_fetch_doc` | doc_id = obj_token |\n| `sheet` | `feishu_sheet` | spreadsheet_token = obj_token |\n| `bitable` | `feishu_bitable_*` 系列 | app_token = obj_token |\n| 其他 | 告知用户暂不支持该类型 | — |\n\n\n### 示例\n\n用户：`帮我看下这个文档 https://xxx.feishu.cn/wiki/ABC123`\n\n1. 调用 `feishu_wiki_space_node`（action: get, token: ABC123）\n2. 返回 `obj_type: \"docx\"`, `obj_token: \"doxcnXYZ789\"`\n3. 调用 `feishu_mcp_fetch_doc`（doc_id: doxcnXYZ789）\n\n## 工具组合\n\n| 需求 | 工具 |\n|------|------|\n| 获取文档文本 | `feishu_mcp_fetch_doc` |\n| 下载图片/文件/画板 | `feishu_doc_media`（action: download） |\n| 解析 wiki token 类型 | `feishu_wiki_space_node`（action: get） |\n| 读写电子表格 | `feishu_sheet` |\n| 操作多维表格 | `feishu_bitable_*` 系列 |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773046878774}}
{"type":"message","id":"91961232","parentId":"2e417a50","timestamp":"2026-03-09T09:01:24.866Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Analyzing document options**\n\nI think I need to fetch the content from the link provided by the user before confirming the options for the slide deck skills. Since the user supplied a docx URL, I could use the feishu_fetch_doc directly to start the analysis. Once I have this content, I can present the user with three choices based on what I find in the document. Let's see how this plays out!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae8c614bcc81938c79c75042aba112\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABproxkzBcT5C08EY3yWTqquxRgnNGdM0l8RAUw8xiCICdg8-KtLjupYZRVIxzmMzjBhdjnVPuGHKrTlp6xjv4z9AVOe18jFZ-dM4NmdMn0GNg5fERqXvc6-Ov8NJouQ5qh_UDt1DKNmsUp5w_kZRMdkh2YZSwlsiuZZqpI6APAyIfz3Mq2buJouxkPAJZJHgSskA2ovp8tr7E_LI-CrtiYAo4oCx1MTHiiYOziDGFtJolRnOUvwUsLcVmu6vXJZZ2bYLD7v4GVBpIqIy2PfAGX38ccqPpcTqrM7pKwV5BSTSAJOWY0BFYLOG7BdLNYu0PCgCKzq8lODtUAhKgTWn1mCnq7mMG0Q9mlGqan_cXe_YlSQ0oLH4gSZvayJU2nWEd2_tkrET4tLuoqVsSYEltjlHHLgds-xh39nQWyqHtGZ9zNaB1_ozB3zyYSiEiZzqigjgeg4Ccev-KGe_-6pNK0j9OwtYGle4lvAiZNRsimyfEnxzLe3rewgAyWeMH1EnqEdkQSUbYsCVzFVGZy2g8jh8FIyBxS3MoEwPTRj9T9ZDI2ibsYhWjpS3nl-VdOih1P2gx1RK1yw8PiKyyj5eu617jaakL_NOCSV7cZO7Ix7e9WNTPIcr6eAQFuFn83YfRD3fp6rulDZa3dXV9DOYEk7Z1L3uSFq3fFrfPaPghARWwLCWodbg4El4-ivpDUGScSzR3H_vaUGIdylH0qgzdR7ucbcLxfGJ6vdApRlMEncFAJEpCvfM58Llc36BtOUB8UyJrp2PEmalKLpuvoJnFrvLH2f0Vw_vb5XOdAgITUq2OXd0Kj8GJaOqWg1UhLLsmoqhOQo62NsD5thqFYVhPtgjuQDnFBWTT_2tG8wQLUAKZV6o0UF4YNHNZPN3re5ZPkz-8kpVpIEoKivYQ7bF1C5pxdMm9LogQt9bIsXdr12OhaISNB6BT66yMzHd0CAaXw7Ti0qo240uEZ2Q1MaBCGugRJjyc-GmMcrfm1ohLMrmNHD7Zr8qoBo8e50uSrtKKVXIzKYWGRndzyt1LdnFi2KohHubFzltlfKeYc0yWpjkNr2DN_SrVgkoId1xGm_N3hA61y\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Analyzing document options**\\n\\nI think I need to fetch the content from the link provided by the user before confirming the options for the slide deck skills. Since the user supplied a docx URL, I could use the feishu_fetch_doc directly to start the analysis. Once I have this content, I can present the user with three choices based on what I find in the document. Let's see how this plays out!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"先把文档内容捞出来，本王看看适合怎么拆成 PPT。","textSignature":"msg_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae8c6431d88193923df7aebc8b28c2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_XqNPLhoSexlOeflMfwYkMmU5|fc_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae8c643e988193adb5bda8003118de","name":"feishu_fetch_doc","arguments":{"doc_id":"https://www.feishu.cn/docx/MkXCd5S4AoP3lbxudpgcqiMInku"},"partialJson":"{\"doc_id\":\"https://www.feishu.cn/docx/MkXCd5S4AoP3lbxudpgcqiMInku\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1034,"output":120,"cacheRead":42496,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43650,"cost":{"input":0.0018095,"output":0.00168,"cacheRead":0.0074367999999999995,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0109263}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773046878781}}
