{"type":"message","id":"37467aea","parentId":"f8c5ea56","timestamp":"2026-03-09T09:02:23.073Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae8c9516d4819394176a206d4c7e98\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABproyWEUcP2kJ5eoqiN3uzez1YrjNF9LTGjElklvn5sjcTjqvNQjO5RxMWzOdA5P7Jz2ZhtuDI1hHpoteysK-baSivZkxYp_7528a6FufG3czU_ypMAOxTPq73yJXGi9oY1QBgWlf5Ihbp1Oy3SK0tYz133kUTKUGC-Hg7cjJ70QvNiNCMIopwNBHat-PjSL6v3EhT0mzPjMdjGXGEbwlejK1joBlFi8ceyge1K2cHT0PcUPFSXOtXN7LBtlVzelwjm9jLya2W84dYvuuevkz4U_KD6_2JQI1ooFAgpp2MXaayfbel0oOjssqM_SabiX2IumD8KWofdWW4mmIW3KQu-xNgySHgQvGA1in1BWk7Q5of2bSqcYKam5JtVVCpkpcMi9gs1K5bFDolLIYq1BrOn3y_ZSln-I17-q5o91sm2FY3GDzGwIOjdsG2Ql6An_0YPQpsVov3MAN3k1s646GMOeMT9zdDqCJdDOi_vdMp7WQjqLCPrrPbyC-dhKu0B8ppFJsq3qHNfD7sAbLIDm3cx3QjiA_AgWmiiDF4xiar-7hp3fVMRojCjs9EGFfDoVp8sYRigcAUKY_b11YCGsZOe7awQ1KzXfdEqSRhmnvfaQ_H0XcdNVx_3fAZNPwCrdoinQHHWDyap114Vgo2zL3Op-060gzfpvAj256mQKsoe4D4tUtX8vhOR7ymQkLAxta1Wd6kOuRPZQ0s1FTVZhRWVjCxhviNg05xODEE30VYjr26n5tG-2aSQSlewt2KnGtdNIOEoXwGvFtAdJly77-MGAU-54_MTD1TenWnPGPWr427J2LCCxPlAA4qjfvZY5bSpV2Nw8MjFPLxfagUnaD4PfDiGsgEzLwsN4a9c9ejmErO9FcSIkHlUehiMOe5Ug7cHJSXJaNLvlLzgRVkV9wiX2wKZmFY5LyRE18cC82ZWfopg-I=\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 那更气人了——本王写的，结果本王现在还被权限挡在门外，飞书这破门禁是真会找事。\n\n但没事，这种情况也不是不能救。\n\n你现在有两个最快办法：\n\n1. 直接把文档内容贴给我\n哪怕分几段贴，本王都能立刻给你整理成 PPT。\n\n2. 你只告诉我这篇文档的主题\n我可以先凭上下文给你反推一版 PPT 结构，再慢慢补细节。\n\n如果你想最快推进，你现在直接回我这 4 个东西就行：\n- 文档主题\n- 主要给谁看\n- 想做多少页\n- 偏演讲型，还是偏招生展示型\n\n你要是懒得打那么多，本王也可以直接先给你起一版通用框架：\n- 封面\n- 背景/问题\n- 核心观点\n- 方法拆解\n- 案例演示\n- 落地路径\n- 总结收束\n\n你把主题甩过来，本王直接开始搭。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae8c9624c481939bcb500db75b6fd4"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1753,"output":282,"cacheRead":42368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44403,"cost":{"input":0.00306775,"output":0.003948,"cacheRead":0.0074144,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01443015}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773046924004}}
