{"type":"message","id":"4ba58acf","parentId":"6a8ea046","timestamp":"2026-03-09T09:08:13.817Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_LZeNPMzn5HwhtTUHx7F5lSKi|fc_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae8df69fc08193b940b6b50c675653","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/ai-partner-crash-fixes/analysis.md","content":"# Analysis\n\n- Topic: 苏神和虾王：那些一起翻过的车，最后都怎么修好了\n- Content Type: 直播分享 / AI 协作复盘 / 方法论输出\n- Audience: General readers（对 AI 智能体、工作流、企业协同感兴趣的人）\n- Language: zh\n- Recommended Style: editorial-infographic\n- Confirmed Style: editorial-infographic（科技感 + 高级简洁）\n- Recommended Slide Count: 12\n- Confirmed Slide Count: 12\n- Review Outline: skipped by user\n- Review Prompts: skipped by user\n\n## Content Signals\n- 真实案例复盘\n- 技术协作与方法论\n- 需要清晰的信息结构和讲故事能力\n- 适合用时间线、闭环图、流程图、对比关系来表达\n\n## Why This Style\neditorial-infographic 适合把复杂技术协作故事拆成清晰、可读、可传播的叙事型页面，兼顾“高级感”和“科技解释力”。"},"partialJson":"{\"file_path\":\"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/ai-partner-crash-fixes/analysis.md\",\"content\":\"# Analysis\\n\\n- Topic: 苏神和虾王：那些一起翻过的车，最后都怎么修好了\\n- Content Type: 直播分享 / AI 协作复盘 / 方法论输出\\n- Audience: General readers（对 AI 智能体、工作流、企业协同感兴趣的人）\\n- Language: zh\\n- Recommended Style: editorial-infographic\\n- Confirmed Style: editorial-infographic（科技感 + 高级简洁）\\n- Recommended Slide Count: 12\\n- Confirmed Slide Count: 12\\n- Review Outline: skipped by user\\n- Review Prompts: skipped by user\\n\\n## Content Signals\\n- 真实案例复盘\\n- 技术协作与方法论\\n- 需要清晰的信息结构和讲故事能力\\n- 适合用时间线、闭环图、流程图、对比关系来表达\\n\\n## Why This Style\\neditorial-infographic 适合把复杂技术协作故事拆成清晰、可读、可传播的叙事型页面，兼顾“高级感”和“科技解释力”。\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":60158,"output":285,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61979,"cost":{"input":0.1052765,"output":0.00399,"cacheRead":0.0002688,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.10953529999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773047284036}}
