Q_WA8QRoprzkTNx_a3Z9f71sLtphw89HzIzHEN4d5Wqs-gRCl0yn8d5cSdmy-eqTnJ0BOZ3hvUlr8yCgZpe8wGP-2bLpMZ2gylXyTe_4sXU0F74aIIOthNpg099u87gNDxuf7ZITRV5o3NsN0r8UMVvkxjCTRvI2qclnWdrmuYNcthC6nvLP4YCKxnLP2z2wZbfmUetQSp8sRFu4ipRTHAM5nRm25ddtish3S3KGmFoxni6S7yXobOLJlWvITu4FPTi7e86rqogYvKQhxyMAXN2Ytk=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering prompt file creation**\\n\\nI need to gather prompt files from an outline. Creating concise prompts manually for each slide could be lengthy since I’d need 12 files. A python script might simplify this process by generating slides from structured JSON. Alternatively, splitting files with a shell script could work too. I think I should write a script that reads the outline, but I might also be able to create 3-4 files manually for speed.\"}]}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_deLCw4PAgBCQ8KOiJh5a56Wl|fc_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae8e5043f48193bea83184301f9408","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom pathlib import Path\nbase = Path('/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/ai-partner-crash-fixes')\n(base/'prompts').mkdir(exist_ok=True)\nstyle = '''<STYLE_INSTRUCTIONS>\nDesign Aesthetic: High-quality magazine explainer aesthetic with clear visual storytelling. The deck should feel like a premium tech publication turning messy real-world AI failures into digestible visual narratives. Clean illustrations, structured layouts, editorial hierarchy, and restrained but confident accent colors.\n\nBackground:\n  Texture: Clean white or light gray background with subtle paper grain only when it helps separate sections.\n  Base Color: Pure White (#FFFFFF) and Light Gray (#F8F9FA)\n\nTypography:\n  Headlines: Bold display serif or modern sans-serif with strong visual presence, editorial sophistication, and high contrast against the background.\n  Body: Humanist sans-serif optimized for reading, clean and professional, readable at medium sizes with comfortable spacing.\n\nColor Palette:\n  Primary Text: Near Black (#1A1A1A) - headlines and body copy\n  Secondary Text: Dark Gray (#4A5568) - captions and supporting labels\n  Background: Pure White (#FFFFFF) - primary background\n  Alt Background: Light Gray (#F8F9FA) - section surfaces and cards\n  Accent 1: Editorial Blue (#2563EB) - diagrams, key pathways, emphasis\n  Accent 2: Coral (#F97316) - problems, errors, failure points\n  Accent 3: Emerald (#10B981) - fixes, successful outcomes\n  Accent 4: Amber (#F59E0B) - warnings, gaps, risks\n  Dividers: Medium Gray (#D1D5DB) - structure lines and separators\n\nVisual Elements:\n  - Clean flat illustrations, never photographic\n  - Structured multi-section editorial layouts\n  - Callout boxes for key insights and memorable quotes\n  - Icon-based system diagrams and workflow arrows\n  - Flow diagrams showing failure -> diagnosis -> fix\n  - Pull quotes and summary boxes for high-impact lines\n  - Minimal but clear chart and matrix components\n\nDensity Guidelines:\n  - Content per slide: 1 core message, 3-5 supporting elements max\n  - Whitespace: controlled and intentional; enough breathing room to keep dense information readable\n\nStyle Rules:\n  Do: Create clear visual narrative flow, use structured layouts, include callout boxes, design metaphors for complex ideas, maintain magazine-quality polish.\n  Don't: Use photographs, create cluttered walls of text, mix visual styles, add purposeless decoration, add slide numbers, footers, or logos.\n</STYLE_INSTRUCTIONS>'''\nslides = [\n('01-slide-cover.md','Slide 1 of 12\\nType: Cover\\nFilename: 01-slide-cover.png\\nHeadline: 苏神和虾王\\nSub-headline: 那些一起翻过的车，最后都怎么修好了\\nNarrative Goal: 让观众立刻知道这是关于真实 AI 协作翻车与修复的高质量复盘。\\nVisual: 杂志封面风，左侧是扁平插画风虾王形象，右侧是聊天窗口、警告图标、修复箭头与系统面板的组合，白底蓝橙点缀。\\nLayout: title-hero，左文右图，大标题醒目。'),\n('02-slide-why-this-talk.md','Slide 2 of 12\\nType: Content\\nFilename: 02-slide-why-this-talk.png\\nHeadline: 这不是一场炫技直播\\nSub-headline: 而是一场真实人机协作复盘\\nBody:\\n- 表层：具体翻车与修复\\n- 中层：AI 助手翻车的根因\\n- 深层：如何养成长期搭子\\nVisual: 三层分层结构图，像冰山/分层架构图，搭配 crash、magnifier、roadmap 图标。\\nLayout: layered-explainer。'),\n('03-slide-five-layers.md','Slide 3 of 12\\nType: Content\\nFilename: 03-slide-five-layers.png\\nHeadline: AI 助手翻车，往往不是一个点坏了\\nSub-headline: 通常是五层里的某几层没有打通\\nBody:\\n- 指令层\\n- 记忆层\\n- 规则层\\n- 工具层\\n- 反馈层\\nVisual: 五段横向连接卡片，带图标和箭头，故障点用橙色标出。\\nLayout: horizontal-process。'),\n('04-slide-identity-mistake.md','Slide 4 of 12\\nType: Content\\nFilename: 04-slide-identity-mistake.png\\nHeadline: 同一句话，谁发出去，性质完全不同\\nSub-headline: 案例一：发消息身份搞错了\\nBody:\\n- 需求简单：去群里艾特某个人\\n- 实际问题：用了用户身份，不是机器人身份\\n- 修复：机器人身份优先、写入记忆、形成纠错纪律\\nVisual: 左右对比卡片，左边机器人身份（安全自动化），右边用户身份（风险更高），中间有错误切换箭头。\\nLayout: comparison-split。'),\n('05-slide-group-boundaries.md','Slide 5 of 12\\nType: Content\\nFilename: 05-slide-group-boundaries.png\\nHeadline: 真正高级的助手，不是会说，而是知道什么时候闭嘴\\nSub-headline: 案例二：群聊规则没收住\\nBody:\\n- 只有被艾特或出现“虾王”才回应\\n- 这是群级行为白名单\\n- 关键修复：写入长期记忆\\nVisual: 群聊界面决策树，只有两个触发条件打开绿色响应路径，其他都灰掉并锁住。\\nLayout: decision-tree。'),\n('06-slide-fake-completion.md','Slide 6 of 12\\nType: Content\\nFilename: 06-slide-fake-completion.png\\nHeadline: AI 最怕的，不是任务难，而是没有完成标准\\nSub-headline: 案例三：心跳任务只做了半套\\nBody:\\n- 只做健康检查就以为完成\\n- 漏掉自拍生成与实际发送\\n- 修复：把动作指令升级成验收标准\\nVisual: 清单式信息图，先显示只勾选第一项的错误状态，再显示四项全完成的正确状态。\\nLayout: process-checklist。'),\n('07-slide-voice-protocol.md','Slide 7 of 12\\nType: Content\\nFilename: 07-slide-voice-protocol.png\\nHeadline: 脑子知道要发语音，不等于真的会发语音\\nSub-headline: 案例四：飞书语音链路没打通\\nBody:\\n- 先生成了音频，但不是语音条\\n- 协议关键：.opus / file_type=opus / msg_type=audio / duration\\n- 最终：固化成可复用脚本\\nVisual: 技术管线图 text -> TTS -> opus -> upload -> audio message，错误分支用橙色，成功链路用绿色。\\nLayout: technical-pipeline。'),\n('08-slide-false-alerts.md','Slide 8 of 12\\nType: Content\\nFilename: 08-slide-false-alerts.png\\nHeadline: 不是所有红色报错，都等于真实故障\\nSub-headline: 案例五：基线校验误报\\nBody:\\n- 现象：openclaw.json 校验 FAILED\\n- 根因：相对路径导致误报\\n- 修复：改绝对路径、改说明、重新校验\\nVisual: 错误分析面板，FAILED 徽标、路径字符串放大镜、相对路径划掉、绝对路径高亮。\\nLayout: problem-solution-panel。'),\n('09-slide-double-truth.md','Slide 9 of 12\\nType: Content\\nFilename: 09-slide-double-truth.png\\nHeadline: 最怕的不是没改，而是只改了一半\\nSub-headline: 案例六：记忆改了，系统配置没改\\nBody:\\n- 记忆说：4 小时一次\\n- 配置说：30m\\n- 真正修复：四层一致\\nVisual: 四层垂直对齐图：口头规则、记忆文件、系统配置、校验结果。先错位，再对齐。\\nLayout: vertical-stack。'),\n('10-slide-plugin-conflict.md','Slide 10 of 12\\nType: Content\\nFilename: 10-slide-plugin-conflict.png\\nHeadline: 很多长期不稳定，不是新东西坏了，而是旧垃圾没清干净\\nSub-headline: 案例七：双插件冲突\\nBody:\\n- 旧版与新版插件残留\\n- duplicate plugin id 持续告警\\n- 修复：移除旧配置、隔离旧目录、再校验\\nVisual: 系统图中两个同 ID 插件盒子碰撞报警，右侧是清理后的单插件稳定状态。\\nLayout: before-after-system。'),\n('11-slide-four-loops.md','Slide 11 of 12\\nType: Content\\nFilename: 11-slide-four-loops.png\\nHeadline: 一个长期搭子，至少要打通四个闭环\\nSub-headline: 这不是“会聊天”，而是“能长期协作”\\nBody:\\n- 指令闭环\\n- 记忆闭环\\n- 执行闭环\\n- 纠错闭环\\nVisual: 圆形四闭环框架图，中心写“长期协作型智能体”，四周四个环以不同强调色围绕。\\nLayout: circular-framework。'),\n('12-slide-back-cover.md','Slide 12 of 12\\nType: Back Cover\\nFilename: 12-slide-back-cover.png\\nHeadline: AI 搭子真正的成熟\\nBody:\\n- 不是从不翻车\\n- 而是每翻一次车\\n- 都比上一次更难再翻同样的车\\nVisual: 极简收尾页，修好的护栏/轨道延伸向远方，虾王小剪影面向前方，蓝白基调，橙色裂痕变为绿色修复线。\\nLayout: quote-closing。')\n]\nbase_prompt = Path('/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/skills/baoyu-slide-deck/references/base-prompt.md').read_text()\nfor name, content in slides:\n    text = f\"{base_prompt}\\n\\n{style}\\n\\n---\\n\\n## SLIDE CONTENT\\n\\n{content}\\n\\nPlease generate a polished 16:9 presentation slide image in Chinese. Keep text concise and legible. Use flat editorial illustration, no photography, no logos, no slide numbers.\"\n    (base/'prompts'/name).write_text(text)\nprint('done', len(slides))\nPY","workdir":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\nbase = Path('/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/ai-partner-crash-fixes')\\n(base/'prompts').mkdir(exist_ok=True)\\nstyle = '''<STYLE_INSTRUCTIONS>\\nDesign Aesthetic: High-quality magazine explainer aesthetic wi