{"type":"message","id":"fe8a0b8c","parentId":"eade6b7f","timestamp":"2026-03-09T09:29:34.372Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Proposing a fix for duplicates**\n\nI realize I need to apologize concisely and suggest a fix, mentioning the likely prompt collision. It might be a good idea to check if files of similar sizes indicate duplicates and ask the user for permission. I can say I've noticed the issue. I should propose regenerating with stricter prompts and consider an outline review. Perhaps I could examine the image content, but I think acknowledging the file sizes is important too, as they suggest suspicious duplicates.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae92ef5ab88193b2391e9ac190a2fc\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABprpL1Ld-rQa5kfA5Z0t3q4I6FWMmD-6wDmkbDdG-tQXu6vp4z7_h-SCKs4WSqC91EMoQF9dTDYQ8v28Z9bqUCwz7HhVRHb6nbmpQxNv5oYophnkRxmF9dhexetqlGeu0X7XewiaigAVLTTVgYSGukl7Jxa6B9_q99lJA-UdH-dnR8VchOvZYQAYln4RIqAhJ69JgMyspQER1XtrDKBEGcDUv5itT4tfxoWiPbmNaoEIZ8HCSQ_EQV_g5_IAKnGifWPSpjqk0bGcWSW6Ngqd-WjVuW0MN9E2M6a9YVn-9ayb7i1vcUoVuYx5OBomsvRpsA3Hzjy4TDoF2jBCIld6ZrHLQY1h15GRJc2XOTzdNO6PudEGjeenYwV6D3tiY0-uXCbYiOmibVWwCJHJpcgS3BaSnKzp0IVk_0TtK8KTO51eTdds2rwwPTlKJA5JsXUL3eowXHwu6i5bR09e3l6kEI21q-XPQoAWmd_szTRARy4FT-0gJvleRL-5sgg3AB8YxdfPYcEucXNtt6oThcM3raRBn32zZoO10ArFQw7DnxwSVBriejN42fHAf-apB3oePax6vbyB65BV32DNGhPpDKBjnVarkm3Gbw6LSru03mLmUlTVPI0UlRyJoz9gA4opcrWkkm40QfEF3a0zMxalR0Dr-K7P_XtPsxP1ZnWlQqlQsYURIARuOqICnvP1CDRn_yxMbmeR77vuh51uUKhE6P5SdLZPNd5d5Rc3_wI7Lqe4d7UJDR73Ti2VrXTVJDp2RjHJC7-ytIiLvutNvQZ6T1yTpGpMmVj6-cmkS17TnzuOYlcJuhenowPYqcPd4HBQt88bVIrlq7jcWWr7i89mu6oYESoIgo8IBwEa1ln_KLAQaR-SKKDvoUXxRfKgKJmTPBNCyxokpiLquM911CxCOr6Ia0cC0limN6LNChlA7ThhYEtqOGV3txpzXtozWMptCFqDv0Z-51rEx7VP_ZG4EVFur7-l4pwa6P2zVDa50H3wY4ilG1esn6nA4rrZyDivLRHd_hj3jVRPR2RAh-XJ71rS92Bn2xpajnw282HtcuRpvG2omJ9xxqX8TrBj5gtuk3uAkwFSSKzq_JNX752ndQxovjyBLc8WVu0HuLHPJ0PzRstpk2Tmm3kQPhurhMnY79a0fpNt0TP9DCkvk7bUrBQjC05rrtMo_MdmF3UgMEgGKodrr5wcgLa6Fy4Erv0K8k6ISa5dJYjItlhDS6XhXVvJDQfQqTA8TWea8ueAcpti9qMKzkuKVeG8nUobqysdbj4_jswSrK8oGZfegO_wm2X_UMApZS1g3HnExGUoZqEfolN77AfoSty2qoa1Evl2zgp_fsfy-afpBATSoOrGL3IoNd5AQ-A4jWbqv5Cd9ZIoTzd0Bj4AaZPRtS8-mT-V6xof-uGry8pLLcVrVHa-iqIL_plcKH3enhBp68Dm63TOCrR7G5miVCJBD6RBQIlx0sepN2LVyGPARk2kUsAhHL8bwVNg==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Proposing a fix for duplicates**\\n\\nI realize I need to apologize concisely and suggest a fix, mentioning the likely prompt collision. It might be a good idea to check if files of similar sizes indicate duplicates and ask the user for permission. I can say I've noticed the issue. I should propose regenerating with stricter prompts and consider an outline review. Perhaps I could examine the image content, but I think acknowledging the file sizes is important too, as they suggest suspicious duplicates.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 对，这次是本王翻大了。\n\n我刚才只盯着“有没有生成成功”，没盯“生成对没对”。\n现在回看，很多页明显是串图/套图了，属于流程跑通了，但成品质量没过关。这锅不甩，算我失职。\n\n问题本质有两个：\n1. 我这次走的是批量生图，图像模型把几页内容混了，导致多页视觉重复、文不对题\n2. 我为了先给你交付，跳过了中间人工验图，这一步本来就不该省\n\n现在正确处理方式不是硬解释，而是重做。\n\n我建议这么修：\n- 保留现有大纲\n- 不直接整套批量出图\n- 改成逐页校验生成\n- 先给你出前 3 页确认风格和质量\n- 你点头后再继续剩下页面\n\n这样才能把这套 PPT 真做对。\n\n如果你同意，本王下一步就直接重做，按这个标准来：\n- 风格更统一：高级简洁 + 科技感\n- 每页严格对应文案，不再让模型自由乱飞\n- 先出 3 页样稿给你验\n\n你回我一句：\n“重做”\n我马上开修，不再拿错图糊弄你。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae92f5798481938880232c316601e0"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1198,"output":410,"cacheRead":73984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75592,"cost":{"input":0.0020965,"output":0.00574,"cacheRead":0.012947199999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0207837}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773048556124}}
