{"type":"message","id":"1042d79c","parentId":"c2ed8a5d","timestamp":"2026-03-09T09:36:06.538Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 重做版已经好了，这次不是那套错图版。\n\n你直接点这个新版：\nhttps://pugmarp5va.feishu.cn/file/BU5sbV7N7owi9KxtTEncsKi3nwh\n\n文件名：\n`ai-partner-crash-fixes-redo.pptx`\n\n这版我改成了“内容结构正确优先”的正式 PPT：\n- 不再用那套会串图的批量生图\n- 每页内容都对应原文逻辑\n- 适合你直接继续改、继续讲、继续美化\n\n我先把锅认清楚：\n上一版是“流程跑通了，成品没过脑子”；\n这一版才是能用的。\n\n你先打开看。\n如果你要，本王下一步继续给你补两种增强版：\n1. 视觉美化版\n2. 演讲精简版（更适合直播讲）🦐","textSignature":"msg_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae9480909881939af89eb5a3a59bc6"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1661,"output":216,"cacheRead":80384,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82261,"cost":{"input":0.00290675,"output":0.0030239999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0140672,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01999795}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773048957915}}
