{"type":"message","id":"639eadb0","parentId":"ed45a334","timestamp":"2026-03-09T09:40:34.794Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to apologize and suggest redoing the image version. Maybe I should get approval for the first three slides before moving forward. It seems like a tighter process could help avoid any issues down the line. Communication is key here! I'll make sure to get feedback early on to keep everything running smoothly. This way, I can ensure the final product meets everyone's expectations. It makes sense to approach it systematically.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae958af89c81938004fcc9a1d1c786\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABprpWOmzyNN2jISTrZlE7Zz3q8UmgE9YbYBZfEcsxD6KjvtVZfdnbbr3BCfmZY_shdGjsyD3sQuy8x04H_RaFbgywMb8Smg2e_TQxefTi8ZXaUGpioRyvLGPxc6emnRrpHTLQg-_4OMurUaJXVwGrYTq37v-p-ygGlCdx9I2PgYWZR36k4etYGkqmVGAm7HdD721YQmFqCvvamwiPj2xdBNKqhLAa9ANIvEqR1JvhT6WSRXnh6fa85U0VjdyszFyyudV8oT-WbTieaCSHclbLLex_0kX5fKzvcVN1Q-ljWOfmKl6zGrOi-gB0793XevTdjI-GVCH036IdRI8RlZx-bWwlTXoZWMQs2c41sJRpNWqdFFFLoWN8Uy-5Dobm-Awcegu84OMU1QviHtVrjxqL07vHN3EoLkX86vn0POwYBbBbJzbEZAJ-tzYVF_cRWcLHZQiGWLAhwvmTVjt5IwMie0cQ18Ms98jhNdvQJ2M61FM8oKn221M3Z72UknWxL9WEG1eJTQ5DWbNZdCE3Alfoz9TVeOlG4UB56prAlMJLP__Zk7gWV_-zlPXI0PArBhHR-H1ge0FH770vLvUM4pWHlWHbreHB6LpcUiLMsVY_nqfLKRLWJvcNVQ4_5NTg7EjaRXW-bbPedjcAwIjYpP5DCDAMa3VG1ylBogYpJNFYp3yRREwlwHI5FA8QYzclo5KRsLsmqbHPfQqium-i6OvFeD_z1148qLqrWsYlTA1jgPL86CobWysSNnXlD60oNWiISqEPl4f8xQtrODZ3aaoBk7kZhfLS8QH0Q9mLxyu4gltwDlzQkb4FaE55zaDe6jCJgL57NRueZvpNy8ifsDQ5re_gZlN3so4UGOtvNeLkVRe5IT_Wvf6fRjm7CsfD1imIqMmczgZ1plxnDrSpclS4URpj-LstllHxIVTPA-mhNtZJGj0_OpYCOy-5p3U6m0dJZBeL7\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"I need to apologize and suggest redoing the image version. Maybe I should get approval for the first three slides before moving forward. It seems like a tighter process could help avoid any issues down the line. Communication is key here! I'll make sure to get feedback early on to keep everything running smoothly. This way, I can ensure the final product meets everyone's expectations. It makes sense to approach it systematically.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 懂了，你要的不是“能用的文字版 PPT”，你要的是那种一眼看上去就有感觉的图片型页面。\n\n那就别绕了，本王给你走正确流程：\n\n这次这样干，才不会再翻车：\n1. 保留现在这版已经整理好的页结构\n2. 改成逐页重做图片\n3. 每做完一页就验一页，不再整套盲跑\n4. 先给你出 3 页样稿：\n   - 封面\n   - 五层翻车框架\n   - 四个闭环总结\n5. 你确认风格对了，我再把剩下页面全部补完\n\n我建议这次图片版风格直接定成：\n- 高级科技感\n- 白底 + 蓝橙强调\n- 杂志信息图风\n- 不是花哨插画，而是“能讲内容”的视觉页\n\n因为你刚才喜欢的，其实是“有视觉冲击”，不是“纯文字堆页”。\n\n你如果同意，本王现在就开始重做图片版样稿。\n你只要回我一句：\n\n“就按这个来”\n\n或者你也可以补一句：\n- 更高级一点\n- 更像课程海报一点\n- 更像 keynote 一点\n\n你一拍板，本王这次一页一页给你修到顺眼为止。🦐","textSignature":"msg_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae958e7e2c81939f02250067435fbe"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":6271,"output":344,"cacheRead":75648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82263,"cost":{"input":0.01097425,"output":0.004816,"cacheRead":0.013238399999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.029028649999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773049223085}}
