{"type":"message","id":"351a19a9","parentId":"134e9324","timestamp":"2026-03-09T09:46:12.602Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Merging files for presentation**\n\nI need to merge files into a PowerPoint (pptx) format and maybe zip them too. It sounds like sending them through a drive would be the best approach. I'll use a script to handle the merging process. I want to remember to rename the files to match the expected pattern, probably something like \"01-slide-final.png\" to keep it organized. Let's take it step by step!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae96e0524081938aac959390b55197\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABprpbj5EruwT-oaZWNXurkZi5-9x9_vrW8as3B-5J-r7LdH-s8r1JIX1bHbOovm0Jnrj1x85l9x57iZ7ADyqkT0ypGFs719fWDjLJdcwexy_4NhQ8C03jsBrNZWbAXhnIIF5Apbq_WKz8rKQiU7bkTeVj1pJCRduMZbUXvnFeMNTilULZyLF-2DydiB8Fa6CGugTg0VWn211TZBKokJH1h3YhXyrOdCsQ-FuBY6b3ic1ZmAfpWIJXBZmYqMQFRkKdHDLF6OFQvrBEkgBwOlVXLf3IFVBZJUbRemZ5vYdg2oWsmJF5bsybwbNsPIGgpHEGxiY035Yr2eFsAE8PoJobEVBQPNa9ZNMf1slOZdH7494LbLB4nrmW24yWKaPiwerwdvf8Fpx6sz9UFOFXtYXlyffUIBkS0s9C020TUKqfy-6dVw8wDOcEUns5UoJljyElmYAkcKISlNVPQ1vAxa__xunHxSESBmvnzzNJ__0G5KCFs7n0F1dcRxw3ithgnQG3yyvsX1-M3Wql7j0a6-J0UFtuYEpmuMRhm6ryNd1JWzB4w7GURFnCC8khlsSybkCGopWojM48NAJLmUwMmJZ5RqEzqPOPz3TbdqaMvpYeZP5p-h4IYLAsiC17Kz5igBZNW0TQ9vJFlF-3xmM_fjnE4ssXk0wh0UxnLJFVqOVc27tLTkZpClxfLk9_LRiSrUpHQ2z4G2gsiR75Wuq5mVugi7FAWHF123XFmTRmrc2fRVp3l7UPXLda5xwDJ_VnQ12qBR8QhkIQL4kMjinN4Yb5ZcsLqCuZcdhlpX6qgKg85HkYnUHci4lYm_S0Yoh5KDUZlZbClesr_qIkGKCNqkKSUogHj8z-QOkjNqFNHDvAv8o_pkqCxSXAay4BBGMjtFLzm7aZWmVJdNgo8VxA6LjPyALa-LRs3m5xuCYg6ZPDoltvNu8Lzqp1k46X9A24ipeEvSff8tyI-nkL7LGrV9z8W_slxpO0JY5C37rGI-cacIBU-1K2B9jdJxZnlrl8qtneEXopj6jqDwTYythB2YSCJAdy8bg==\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Merging files for presentation**\\n\\nI need to merge files into a PowerPoint (pptx) format and maybe zip them too. It sounds like sending them through a drive would be the best 