{"type":"message","id":"70a23854","parentId":"75ea1b7d","timestamp":"2026-03-09T09:46:47.044Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好了，这次是你要的图片版成品，已经全做完了。\n\n1）图片版 PPT：\nhttps://pugmarp5va.feishu.cn/file/QpRDbVCLQoRr4LxixDpcziS9n0f\n\n2）全部 PNG 页面打包：\nhttps://pugmarp5va.feishu.cn/file/Erl6bWFhgoQtyUxcfT4cHiQVnxb\n\n说明一下，这次本王换了做法：\n- 不再用那套会串题的 AI 批量生图\n- 直接重做成统一风格的图片页\n- 每页内容都跟文档逻辑对应\n- 最后再合成 PPT\n\n所以这版的重点是：\n“稳定、对题、能直接用”\n\n你先看。\n如果还要，我下一步可以继续给你做两种升级：\n- 更高级更像发布会的版本\n- 更适合直播投屏的版本（字更大、节奏更强）🦐","textSignature":"msg_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae96ff78048193b82397b68cacdd10"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1954,"output":235,"cacheRead":92544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94733,"cost":{"input":0.0034195,"output":0.00329,"cacheRead":0.0161952,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0229047}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773049597785}}
