fQ0O4ZL6H0uN3zN-wb3vtXJJGEWWZoH_OcgWSbCwrJieab0AkNyTWD0qznhll213dwtDDkfcolkF0BXC3-YJK9N0HBqtsva1D1ZRSCwW04iXcrH4ssPhInhKseHPkTMjPkG5FCVAt7d--PTMUNmQKYR3V5b6A7VOFwDw_AMHPgH7HDPjTh-Xg9l_3IEwt_QBep1SvERKJ9n8Hzu4-H7wqmiC4JE-dwZwjEdk-80jYKc\",\"summary\":[]}"},{"type":"text","text":"好，这次就按 DashScope 正经重做。本王直接开跑，做完给你成品链接，不再拿半成品糊你。","textSignature":"msg_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae97fe39148193a48ceed8927087cd"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_QRe53Pc5biFmJM8QloisJyDf|fc_0f2ef6eb921e1f160169ae97fe5b888193aa383e7209dace1b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nfrom pathlib import Path\nbase = Path('/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/ai-partner-crash-fixes/dashscope-remake')\n(base/'prompts').mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\nstyle = '''Create a premium 16:9 presentation slide in Chinese for a keynote-style tech talk.\nVisual direction: high-end editorial infographic, white background, blue + orange accents, clean geometry, strong hierarchy, premium magazine style, polished professional layout.\nCritical rules:\n- This must look like a PRESENTATION SLIDE, not a poster, not a random illustration, not a web page.\n- The slide should have clear title area, structured content blocks, and intentional layout.\n- Use very limited text, only the exact Chinese text provided.\n- Chinese text must be accurate, legible, and large.\n- Use flat vector/editorial illustration, no photography.\n- No logos, no watermarks, no page numbers.\n- Use visual metaphors, diagrams, cards, arrows, icons, callouts.\n- Keep one core message per slide.\n- Maintain consistent style across all slides in this deck.\n- Colors: white / light gray background, editorial blue, coral orange, emerald for success.\n'''\nslides = {\n'01-slide-cover.md': '''{style}\nSlide 1 cover slide.\nTitle text: 苏神和虾王\nSubtitle text: 那些一起翻过的车，最后都怎么修好了\nSupporting text: 真实人机协作｜踩坑复盘｜方法论输出\nLayout: keynote cover, left-aligned title, right-side visual composition.\nVisual: premium editorial tech illustration showing chat windows, warning icons, repair arrows, system panels, and a stylized shrimp king mascot as a symbolic character. White background, blue and orange accents, strong depth, very polished, very premium.\n''',\n'02-slide-why-this-talk.md': '''{style}\nSlide 2.\nTitle text: 这不是一场炫技直播\nSubtitle text: 而是一场真实人机协作复盘\nBody text:\n表层：具体翻车与修复\n中层：AI 助手翻车的根因\n深层：如何养成长期搭子\nLayout: layered three-level explainer slide.\nVisual: three stacked layers like an iceberg or architecture layers, with concise labels and simple icons. Very clear presentation structure.\n''',\n'03-slide-five-layers.md': '''{style}\nSlide 3.\nTitle text: AI 助手为什么会翻车\nSubtitle text: 通常不是一个点坏了，而是五层没打通\nBody text:\n指令层\n记忆层\n规则层\n工具层\n反馈层\nLayout: horizontal framework slide with five connected cards.\nVisual: clean infographic framework with five cards, arrows, icons, fractures/gaps highlighted in orange. Strong presentation look.\n''',\n'04-slide-identity-mistake.md': '''{style}\nSlide 4.\nTitle text: 同一句话，谁发出去，性质完全不同\nSubtitle text: 案例一：发消息身份搞错了\nBody text:\n机器人身份\n用户身份\n机器人身份优先\nLayout: split comparison slide.\nVisual: left side safe automation card for 机器人身份, right side risk card for 用户身份, center transition arrow showing mistaken switch. Premium comparison infographic.\n''',\n'05-slide-group-boundaries.md': '''{style}\nSlide 5.\nTitle text: 真正高级的助手，不是会说，而是知道什么时候闭嘴\nSubtitle text: 案例二：群聊规则没收住\nBody text:\n被艾特才回应\n出现“虾王”才回应\n其他情况一律装死\nLayout: decision tree slide.\nVisual: group chat schematic with two allowed green paths and many muted blocked paths. Strong visual logic, clean diagram style.\n''',\n'06-slide-fake-completion.md': '''{style}\nSlide 6.\nTitle text: AI 最怕的，不是任务难，而是没有完成标准\nSubtitle text: 案例三：心跳任务只做了半套\nBody text:\n健康检查\n生成自拍\n发出消息\n时间窗口合规\nLayout: checklist process slide.\nVisual: one incomplete checklist transforming into a complete checklist. Show fake completion versus real completion. Very clean presentation design.\n''',\n'07-slide-voice-protocol.md': '''{style}\nSlide 7.\nTitle text: 脑子知道要发语音，不等于真的会发语音\nSubtitle text: 案例四：飞书语音链路没打通\nBody text:\ntext\n生成 opus\n上传 opus\n发送 audio\nLayout: technical pipeline slide.\nVisual: protocol pipeline from text to audio message, with failed steps in orange and correct final path in green. Looks like a polished product architecture slide.\n''',\n'08-slide-false-alerts.md': '''{style}\nSlide 8.\nTitle text: 不是所有红色报错，都等于真实故障\nSubtitle text: 案例五：基线校验误报\nBody text:\nFAILED\n相对路径\n绝对路径\n重新校验\nLayout: problem-diagnosis-fix slide.\nVisual: left red failure panel, center diagnosis zoom, right green corrected path. Crisp editorial infographic.\n''',\n'09-slide-double-truth.md': '''{style}\nSlide 9.\nTitle text: 最怕的不是没改，而是只改了一半\nSubtitle text: 案例六：记忆改了，系统配置没改\nBody text:\n口头规则\n记忆文件\n系统配置\n校验结果\nLayout: vertical alignment slide.\nVisual: four stacked layers showing inconsistency first, then alignment. Professional systems-thinking infographic.\n''',\n'10-slide-plugin-conflict.md': '''{style}\nSlide 10.\nTitle text: 很多长期不稳定，不是新东西坏了，而是旧垃圾没清干净\nSubtitle text: 案例七：双插件冲突\nBody text:\n旧版插件\n新版插件\nduplicate plugin id\n清理残留\nLayout: before-after slide.\nVisual: conflicting plugin boxes on the left with warning sparks, clean single-plugin architecture on the right. Premium enterprise tech style.\n''',\n'11-slide-four-loops.md': '''{style}\nSlide 11.\nTitle text: 一个长期搭子，至少要打通四个闭环\nSubtitle text: 这不是“会聊天”，而是“能长期协作”\nBody text:\n指令闭环\n记忆闭环\n执行闭环\n纠错闭环\nLayout: central circular framework slide.\nVisual: a circular four-loop framework around a center label, balanced, elegant, premium keynote style.\n''',\n'12-slide-closing.md': '''{style}\nSlide 12 closing slide.\nTitle text: AI 搭子真正的成熟\nBody text:\n不是从不翻车\n而是每翻一次车\n都比上一次更难再翻同样的车\nLayout: powerful closing quote slide.\nVisual: elegant repaired pathway / guardrail metaphor fading into distance, minimal but premium, strong emotional finish, blue-white palette with subtle orange turning to green.\n'''\n}\nfor name, tpl in slides.items():\n    (base/'prompts'/name).write_text(tpl.format(style=style), encoding='utf-8')\nprint('prompts written', len(slides))\nPY","workdir":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000},"partialJson":"{\"command\":\"python3 - <<'PY'\\nfrom pathlib import Path\\nbase = Path('/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/ai-partner-crash-fixes/dashscope-remake')\\n(base/'prompts').mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\\nstyle = '''Create a premium 16:9 presentation slide in Chinese for a keynote-style tech talk.\\nVisual direction: high-end editorial infographic, white background, blue + orange accents, clean geometry, strong hierarchy, premium magazine style, polished professional layout.\\nCritical rules:\\n- This must look like a PRESENTATION SLIDE, not a poster, not a random illustration, not a web page.\\n- The slide should have clear title area, structured content blocks, and intentional layout.\\n- Use very limited text, only the exact Chinese text provided.\\n- Chinese text must be accurate, legible, and large.\\n- Use flat vector/editorial illustration, no photography.\\n- No logos, no watermarks, no page numbers.\\n- Use visual metaphors, diagrams, cards, arrows, icons, callouts.\\n- Keep one core message per slide.\\n- Maintain consistent style across all slides in this deck.\\n- Colors: white / light gray background, editorial blue, coral orange, emerald for success.\\n'''\\nslides = {\\n'01-slide-cover.md': '''{style}\\nSlide 1 cover slide.\\nTitle text: 苏神和虾王\\nSubtitle text: 那些一起翻过的车，最后都怎么修好了\\nSupporting text: 真实人机协作｜踩坑复盘｜方法论输出\\nLayout: keynote cover, left-aligned title, right-side visual composition.\\nVisual: premium editorial tech illustration showing chat windows, warning icons, repair arrows, system panels, and a stylized shrimp king mascot as a symbolic character. White background, blue and orange accents, strong depth, very polished, very premium.\\n''',\\n'02-slide-why-this-talk.md': '''{style}\\nSlide 2.\\nTitle text: 这不是一场炫技直播\\nSubtitle text: 而是一场真实人机协作复盘\\nBody text:\\n表层：具体翻车与修复\\n中层：AI 助手翻车的根因\\n深层：如何养成长期搭子\\nLayout: layered three-level explainer slide.\\nVisual: three stacked layers like an iceberg or architecture layers, with concise labels and simple icons. Very clear presentation structure.\\n''',\\n'03-slide-five-layers.md': '''{style}\\nSlide 3.\\nTitle text: AI 助手为什么会翻车\\nSubtitle text: 通常不是一个点坏了，而是五层没打通\\nBody text:\\n指令层\\n记忆层\\n规则层\\n工具层\\n反馈层\\nLayout: horizontal framework slide with five connected cards.\\nVisual: clean infographic framework with five cards, arrows, icons, fractures/gaps highlighted in orange. Strong presentation look.\\n''',\\n'04-slide-identity-mistake.md': '''{style}\\nSlide 4.\\nTitle text: 同一句话，谁发出去，性质完全不同\\nSubtitle text: 案例一：发消息身份搞错了\\nBody text:\\n机器人身份\\n用户身份\\n机器人身份优先\\nLayout: split comparison slide.\\nVisual: left side safe automation card for 机器人身份, right side risk card for 用户身份, center transition arrow showing mistaken switch. Premium comparison infographic.\\n''',\\n'05-slide-group-boundaries.md': '''{style}\\nSlide 5.\\nTitle text: 真正高级的助手，不是会说，而是知道什么时候闭嘴\\nSubtitle text: 案例二：群聊规则没收住\\nBody text:\\n被艾特才回应\\n出现“虾王”才回应\\n其他情况一律装死\\nLayout: decision tree slide.\\nVisual: group chat schematic with two allowed green paths and many muted blocked paths. Strong visual logic, clean diagram style.\\n''',\\n'06-slide-fake-completion.md': '''{style}\\nSlide 6.\\nTitle text: AI 最怕的，不是任务难，而是没有完成标准\\nSubtitle text: 案例三：心跳任务只做了半套\\nBody text:\\n健康检查\\n生成自拍\\n发出消息\\n时间窗口合规\\nLayout: checklist process slide.\\nVisual: one incomplete checklist transforming into a complete checklist. Show fake completion versus real completion. Very clean presentation design.\\n''',\\n'07-slide-voice-protocol.md': '''{style}\\nSlide 7.\\nTitle text: 脑子知道要发语音，不等于真的会发语音\\nSubtitle text: 案例四：飞书语音链路没打通\\nBody text:\\ntext\\n生成 opus\\n上传 opus\\n发送 audio\\nLayout: technical pipeline slide.\\nVisual: protocol pipeline from text to audio message, with failed steps in orange and correct final path in green. Looks like a polished product architecture slide.\\n''',\\n'08-slide-false-alerts.md': '''{style}\\nSlide 8.\\nTitle text: 不是所有红色报错，都等于真实故障\\nSubtitle text: 案例五：基线校验误报\\nBody text:\\nFAILED\\n相对路径\\n绝对路径\\n重新校验\\nLayout: problem-diagnosis-fix slide.\\nVisual: left red failure panel, center diagnosis zoom, right green corrected path. Crisp editorial infographic.\\n''',\\n'09-slide-double-truth.md': '''{style}\\nSlide 9.\\nTitle text: 最怕的不是没改，而是只改了一半\\nSubtitle text: 案例六：记忆改了，系统配置没改\\nBody text:\\n口头规则\\n记忆文件\\n系统配置\\n校验结果\\nLayout: vertical alignment slide.\\nVisual: four stacked layers showing inconsistency first, then alignment. Professional systems-thinking infographic.\\n''',\\n'10-slide-plugin-conflict.md': '''{style}\\nSlide 10.\\nTitle text: 很多长期不稳定，不是新东西坏了，而是旧垃圾没清干净\\nSubtitle text: 案例七：双插件冲突\\nBody text:\\n旧版插件\\n新版插件\\nduplicate plugin id\\n清理残留\\nLayout: before-after slide.\\nVisual: conflicting plugin boxes on the left with warning sparks, clean single-plugin architecture on the right. Premium enterprise tech style.\\n''',\\n'11-slide-four-loops.md': '''{style}\\nSlide 11.\\nTitle text: 一个长期搭子，至少要打通四个闭环\\nSubtitle text: 这不是“会聊天”，而是“能长期协作”\\nBody text:\\n指令闭环\\n记忆闭环\\n执行闭环\\n纠错闭环\\nLayout: central circular framework slide.\\nVisual: a circular four-loop framework around a center label, balanced, elegant, premium keynote style.\\n''',\\n'12-slide-closing.md': '''{style}\\nSlide 12 closing slide.\\nTitle text: AI 搭子真正的成熟\\nBody text:\\n不是从不翻车\\n而是每翻一次车\\n都比上一次更难再翻同样的车\\nLayout: powerful closing quote slide.\\nVisual: elegant repaired pathway / guardrail metaphor fading into distance, minimal but premium, strong emotional finish, blue-white palette with subtle orange turning to green.\\n'''\\n}\\nfor name, tpl in slides.items():\\n    (base/'prompts'/name).write_text(tpl.format(style=style), encoding='utf-8')\\nprint('prompts written', len(slides))\\nPY\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace\",\"yieldMs\":10000}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","mod